text: Mokhlesur Rahman (–12 September 2016) is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Dinajpur-3. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Dinajpur-3 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:1940s births Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:2016 deaths
title: Mokhlesur Rahman
